Nynex Business InformationSystems Co said it won a contract valued at nine mln dlrs fromthe U.S. Army Corp of Engineers to provide an advancedcommunications system for a facility in upstate New York.    The company, a unit of Nynex Corp, said the contract wasfor initial work on the project at the new Fort Drum LightInfantry Post near Watertown, about 65 miles north of Syracuse. Reuter&#3;